    <section id="tribute-info">
      <h2>Major Events in Derek's Life</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>1969</strong> - Born in California</li>
        <li><strong>1987</strong> - Started Berklee College of Music in Boston</li>
        <li><strong>1997</strong> - Started <a href="https://cdbaby.com/">CD Baby</a></li>
        <li><strong>2008</strong> - Moved to San Francisco, sold CD Baby and HostBaby</li>
        <li><strong>2011</strong> - Published “Anything You Want”</li>
        <li><strong>Today</strong> - Derek currently lives in Oxford, England.</li>
      </ul>
    </section>
    <section id="why">
      <h2>Why I picked Derek to write a tribute page to</h2>
        <p>I first learned about Derek while listening to Tim Ferriss's podcast.
        </p><p>
          At the very end of the episode, Derek tells listeners that they can email him directly to his personal email. Tim jokes about how his mailbox will be flooded, but Derek assures that he will respond to every single one.
        </p><p>
          I see this as a challenge and decide to reach out to him, believing surely that he won't respond.
        </p><p>
          Sure enough, I get a response.
        </p><p>
          I've been a fan ever since. Thanks, Derek.
        </p>
    </section>
    <section id="external-link">
